t call by honouring her with many roles. Her talent and looks have not only distinguished as a star to watch but also as a highly in demand diva. After “The Investigator” she has gone to show her class in other films like King’s Wife; Mr Arrogant; Chisom The Wife Material, Too Hard To Forget; Mrs and The Mistress and many more. Luchy Donalds is yet to produce a movie of her own as she enjoys being in front of the camera for now more than anything. And her talent hasn’t gone unnoticed as she has won Nigerian Achievers Award. Vanguard Vulnerably beautiful and sexy, Chiamaka Nwokeukwu, isn’t a household name in Nollywood. But the fair-complexioned actress is very much on her way as she is having the best run of good streak in her career. Her top draw performance in the film, Chinelo, The Shy Virgin, opened not only another… April 26, 2015 In "Entertainment" Sexy and beautiful Yoruba actress, Temitope Abosede Adedapo has taken a subtle swipe at women who go as far as naked to show they are sexy. In a chat with Potpourri, Temitope said she believes a woman should flaunt her God-given endowment but not to the extent of showing off… June 21, 2020 In "Entertainment" Two things make an actor stand out in the movie industry all across the world ; beauty and talent. And one actress seems to have the two handy plus a little more – attitude. The name is Luchy Donalds, a delicate beauty that has gently imprinted her name on the… November 2, 2017 In "News"